<div style="width: 52px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Ambox_style.png" class="image" title="Ambox style.png"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/d/d6/Ambox_style.png" width="40" height="40" border="0" /></a></div>
</td>
<td class="mbox-text" style="">This article <b>may be <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Article_size" title="Wikipedia:Article size">too long</a> to comfortably read and navigate.</b> Please consider splitting content into sub-articles and using this article for a <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Summary_style" title="Wikipedia:Summary style">summary</a> of the key points of the subject.</td>
