<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=E-mail_spam&amp;action=edit&amp;section=42" title="Edit section: External links">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">External links</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Spam info
<ul>
<li><a href="http://spam.abuse.net" class="external text" title="http://spam.abuse.net" rel="nofollow">Spam.Abuse.Net</a></li>
