</ul>
</li>
<li>Spam reports
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.barracudacentral.com/index.cgi?p=spam" class="external text" title="http://www.barracudacentral.com/index.cgi?p=spam" rel="nofollow">Worldwide Email Threat Activity</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Government reports and industry white papers
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.ftc.gov/opa/2005/11/spamharvest.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.ftc.gov/opa/2005/11/spamharvest.pdf" rel="nofollow"><i>Email Address Harvesting and the Effectiveness of Anti-SPAM Filters</i></a> by US FTC, Retrieved on 13-Oct-2007.</li>
