</ul>
</li>
<li>from the author of <a href="/wiki/Pegasus_Mail" title="Pegasus Mail">Pegasus Mail</a> &amp; <a href="/wiki/Mercury_Mail_Transport_System" title="Mercury Mail Transport System">Mercury Mail Transport System</a> - <a href="/wiki/David_Harris_(software_developer)" title="David Harris (software developer)">David Harris</a>
<ul>
